thread.title: D...B..

author: D...B..
title: D...B..
text: Using the service to call the Philippines can make you pull out all of your hair. Many times it does not connect, or it takes over 3 min to get a call to connect. Multiple times it not only connected to the wrong number, but to the wrong country. The sound quality is poor except the rare occasion when it is actually half way decent. The site only post positive reviews with no way of posting your own review, which leads me to believe the reviews are fake, or filtered to show only positives.
